locality: Parc National de Mantady. A 14 km de l'usine de graphite, sur le côté E du sentier à. Forêt Dense Humide Sempervirente. Récolté avec B. Lewis, I. Van Neck, M. Andrianarisata et M. Randriambololona

Andapa District: Bealampona Canton: Befingitra Village. Anjanaharibe-Sud Special Reserve. Along footpath from Campsite 2 (Ambatomainty) heading northwest to Campsite 3 (Ambodinajanaharibe). In moist, evergreen forest along east-west running ridge and adjacent steep slopes. Soils generally loamy, with humus layer and quartz and granite deposits. Specimens collected in alcohol.
Ambatovy: Région Alaotra Mangoro, District Moramanga.
